These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, almond-milk, milk, juice
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, ferret, pony
1. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
5. the person drinking fanta is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | fanta | almond-milk | juice | milk |
| Pet        | chinchilla | fish   | pony | ferret    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, martial-arts, western, sports
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, indian, chinese, american
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the colombian is on the left of the chinese##1
3. the chinese is in an odd position##4
4. the colombian is the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the indian is on the right of the chinese##1
6. the colombian is the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | western | thriller  | martial-arts  | sports |
| Nationality   | american    | colombian | chinese | indian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: corn, tomato, cranberry, peach
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, thriller, action, drama
1. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
2. the person eating cranberry is in an even position##4
3. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person eating tomato##3
4. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
5. the person watching crime movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | peach | cranberry | tomato    | corn      |
| Movie-Genre   | action        | drama     | crime | thriller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, video-games, magic-tricks, singing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, salsa, soul, country
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the fan of classical and the fan of country##2
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the fan of soul is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of country##1
5. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | singing | collecting | video-games | magic-tricks |
| Music-Genre   | soul       | classical   | salsa    | country  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, disco, techno, classical
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, brazilian, japanese, italian
1. the fan of techno is on the right of the italian##1
2. the brazilian is the fan of classical##1
3. the japanese is on the right of the fan of funk##1
4. the fan of disco is on the far left##1
5. the fan of techno is in an odd position##4
6. the indonesian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | disco  | funk    | techno   | classical       |
| Nationality   | indonesian | italian | japanese | brazilian |

