.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, family, superhero, western
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, argentine, chinese, australian
1. the argentine is in an even position##4
2. the person watching western movies is on the right of the argentine##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is in an odd position##4
4. the pakistani is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
5. the chinese is on the left or right of the pakistani##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero      | family | western | fantasy |
| Nationality   | australian | argentine     | pakistani  | chinese  |

