.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, action, spy, time-travel
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, boat, airplane, jet-ski
1. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is the person watching scientific movies##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
6. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | time-travel | spy | action    |
| Transport     | jet-ski | airplane  | taxi     | boat |

