.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, analyst, architect, freelancer
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, rabbit, dog, ferret
1. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the analyst##3
2. the freelancer is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the freelancer##3
4. the freelancer is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
5. the journalist is between the freelancer and the analyst##2
6. the owner of the rabbit is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the rabbit is between the journalist and the owner of the dog##2
8. the journalist is on the left or right of the analyst##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | analyst | journalist      | freelancer | architect |
| Pet   | hedgehog  | ferret | rabbit    | dog            |

