.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, artichoke, asparagus, peas
4 different pets are kept: snake, chinchilla, lizard, rat
1. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
2. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
3. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person eating asparagus##2
4. the owner of the snake is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating asparagus is the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | peas | artichoke   | banana | asparagus |
| Pet    | rat     | chinchilla | snake     | lizard  |

