.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate, sprite, fanta
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, reggae, r&b, hip-hop
1. the person drinking iced-tea is the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the fan of metal is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is between the fan of metal and the person drinking sprite##2
4. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate       | sprite   | iced-tea | fanta |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | reggae | hip-hop        | metal    |

