.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, lemonade, almond-milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, parkour, volleyball, badminton
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk   | almond-milk   | mirinda      | lemonade      |
| Sport      | parkour | volleyball | badminton | weightlifting |

