2. the fan of rock is in an even position##4
3. the person eating plum is in an even position##4
4. the person eating lime is on the far right##1
5. the person eating potato is between the fan of pop and the fan of rock##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | spinach | plum  | potato  | lime |
| Music-Genre   | blues  | rock | d&b | pop   |

