.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, filmmaking, puzzles, rock-climbing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, lacrosse, sailing, surfing
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | filmmaking         | gardening   | puzzles |
| Sport   | sailing    | lacrosse | surfing | skiing   |

