.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, fishing, gardening, drawing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, golf, weightlifting, handball
1. the person who's sport is handball is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | fishing | hiking | gardening    | drawing |
| Sport   | surfing   | weightlifting  | handball | golf     |

