.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, traveling, skydiving, dancing
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, canadian, australian, dutch
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4
3. the canadian is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
4. the australian is on the left or right of the canadian##3
5. the canadian is between the dutch and the australian##2
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby         | dancing   | skydiving | magic-tricks | traveling    |
| Nationality   | australian | canadian  | dutch     | thai |

