.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, coffee, hot-chocolate, cola
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, plum, pumpkin, lemon
1. the person eating plum is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
3. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
5. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
6. the person eating pumpkin is in an even position##4
7. the person eating artichoke is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | cola | soy-milk    | hot-chocolate       | coffee |
| Food       | plum  | pumpkin | lemon | artichoke  |

