.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, russian, chinese, australian
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, skateboard, roller, bike
1. the japanese is on the left of the australian##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the chinese##1
5. the japanese is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
6. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | russian | chinese | japanese  | australian |
| Transport     | scooter      | roller       | skateboard | bike     |

