.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, lawyer, scientist, social-worker
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, scooter, bike, snowmobile
1. the lawyer is in an even position##4
2. the lawyer is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
3. the person driving the scooter is between the dressmaker and the person driving the skateboard##2
4. the lawyer is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the bike is on the right of the social-worker##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | dressmaker | scientist   | social-worker | lawyer |
| Transport   | snowmobile          | scooter | skateboard         | bike  |

 